videos.description: Jaime Echenique breaks a near 7-minute scoring drought for Wichita State as he bullies his defender into the paint and soars for a slam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Echenique flushes it home for Wichita State) 2020/3/5

videos.headline: Echenique flushes it home for Wichita State

videos.description: Wichita State's Dexter Dennis uses his body as he makes his way to the hoop, lays in a tough jumper and draws a foul on Memphis.
videos.headline: Dennis maneuvers for key and-1

videos.description: Alex Lomax drives in from the corner and fires a wraparound pass to Isaiah Maurice who finishes with a Memphis layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Lomax's beautiful assist powers Maurice's bucket for Memphis) 2020/3/5

videos.headline: Lomax's beautiful assist powers Maurice's bucket for Memphis

videos.description: Tyler Harris caps off the first half with a deep 3-pointer for Memphis, knocking in the Tigers' sixth triple of the half.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Memphis' Harris beats the halftime buzzer with 3) 2020/3/5

videos.headline: Memphis' Harris beats the halftime buzzer with 3

videos.description: Memphis' Dexter Dennis fights for the steal and Jamarius Burton is the beneficiary, showing off his athleticism with a second-half bucket.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Dennis' hustle leads to Burton's circus shot) 2020/3/5

videos.headline: Dennis' hustle leads to Burton's circus shot

videos.description: Precious Achiuwa hauls in the pass from Tyler Harris and brings it down to gain control, he then rises up for a powerful baseline slam to record a double-double.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Achiuwa hammers home a baseline jam) 2020/3/5

videos.headline: Achiuwa hammers home a baseline jam

videos.description: Precious Achiuwa and Tyler Harris run the fast break, then Achiuwa rises up after the give-and-go for a powerful slam vs. Wichita State.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Achiuwa rocks the rim with authority) 2020/3/5

videos.headline: Achiuwa rocks the rim with authority
